descriptionHtml:
Selene from underworld. Well tried hard to get her look a like but Atm it\'s too hard to do with skyrim edit:) (there should be sliders for the mouth and forehead and better noses) Still shes a nord lvl1 in helgen keep. There is 2 choises: non vampire and vampire save. Hope you like her anyways:DD 

mods you need to get her look a like:

Hair is from \"Tera Hair pack\" and i think that can\'t be found in nexus so google it;)  

Better Females by Bella: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812
(load main file then the makeup version 1.)

BFG-better face Gen: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6953

Flans Eyes for Skyrim: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14539
(just recommended)

Enchaned Character Edit:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12951
(replaces sliders for eyes and nose So you can tilt the eyes and edit nose width) 

If you get the vampire save:
Female Vampires Have Fangs:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22522
	
Underworld Dawnguard - Vampire and Werewolf Eyes:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/22619

For the ENB:
sharpshooters ENB: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15105
And might need dawnguard cos of vampire armor.

:))
